    <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#333333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">Dear colleague,</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#333333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">We are delighted to share the <strong>Electoral Members&rsquo; Network programme for 2026</strong> &mdash; a year of knowledge-sharing, global dialogue, and recognition of excellence in electoral administration.</p>

    <!-- Awards section -->
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 24px 0; background-color:#f0f4f8; border-radius:6px; border-left:4px solid #1a2744;">
    <tr><td style="padding: 20px 24px;">
        <p style="margin:0 0 4px; color:#1a2744; font-size:16px; font-weight:700;">22nd International Electoral Awards &amp; Symposium</p>
        <p style="margin:4px 0 12px; color:#555; font-size:14px;">29 November &ndash; 3 December 2026 &nbsp;|&nbsp; The Manila Hotel, Philippines</p>
        <p style="margin:0 0 12px; color:#333; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6;">Co-hosted by <strong>ICPS</strong> and the <strong>Commission on Elections of the Philippines (COMELEC)</strong>, the 22nd International Electoral Awards will bring together electoral leaders from across the globe for five days of cultural exchange, high-level discussion, and the prestigious Awards Ceremony.</p>
        <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
            <tr>
                <td style="padding:4px 16px 4px 0; color:#666; font-size:14px; vertical-align:top; white-space:nowrap;"><strong>Cost:</strong></td>
                <td style="padding:4px 0; color:#333; font-size:14px;">Free &mdash; no registration fee</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="padding:4px 16px 4px 0; color:#666; font-size:14px; vertical-align:top; white-space:nowrap;"><strong>Accommodation:</strong></td>
                <td style="padding:4px 0; color:#333; font-size:14px;">Provided for all delegates at The Manila Hotel</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td style="padding:4px 16px 4px 0; color:#666; font-size:14px; vertical-align:top; white-space:nowrap;"><strong>Nominations:</strong></td>
                <td style="padding:4px 0; color:#333; font-size:14px;">Opening April 2026</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </td></tr>
