    <!-- Webinar series -->
    <p style="margin:0 0 12px; color:#1a2744; font-size:16px; font-weight:700;">2026 Webinar Series</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#333333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">Alongside the Awards, we are running three in-depth webinars throughout the year, open to all Network members. All sessions run from <strong>14:00 to 16:00 UTC</strong> via Zoom.</p>

    <!-- Webinar 1 -->
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0 0 16px; background-color:#f0f4f8; border-radius:6px; border-left:4px solid #e8a317;">
    <tr><td style="padding: 16px 20px;">
        <p style="margin:0 0 2px; color:#1a2744; font-size:14px; font-weight:700;">Webinar 1 &mdash; Friday, 10 April 2026</p>
        <p style="margin:0 0 8px; color:#333; font-size:14px; font-weight:600;">Empowering the Election Workforce</p>
        <p style="margin:0; color:#555; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5;">Global survey findings across 26 jurisdictions on recruitment, training, and retention challenges facing Election Management Bodies.</p>
    </td></tr>
    </table>

    <!-- Webinar 2 -->
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0 0 16px; background-color:#f0f4f8; border-radius:6px; border-left:4px solid #e8a317;">
    <tr><td style="padding: 16px 20px;">
        <p style="margin:0 0 2px; color:#1a2744; font-size:14px; font-weight:700;">Webinar 2 &mdash; Thursday, 11 June 2026</p>
        <p style="margin:0 0 8px; color:#333; font-size:14px; font-weight:600;">Speed in Election Results Transmission</p>
        <p style="margin:0; color:#555; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5;">End-to-end results workflows, transparency mechanisms, and public communication during results consolidation.</p>
    </td></tr>
    </table>

    <!-- Webinar 3 -->
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0 0 24px; background-color:#f0f4f8; border-radius:6px; border-left:4px solid #e8a317;">
    <tr><td style="padding: 16px 20px;">
        <p style="margin:0 0 2px; color:#1a2744; font-size:14px; font-weight:700;">Webinar 3 &mdash; Wednesday, 16 September 2026</p>
        <p style="margin:0 0 8px; color:#333; font-size:14px; font-weight:600;">Inclusive Elections: Ensuring the Right to Vote for All</p>
        <p style="margin:0; color:#555; font-size:13px; line-height:1.5;">Voter-centred design, accessibility, frontline staff training, and preserving independence and secrecy of the vote.</p>
    </td></tr>
    </table>

