    <!-- 2025 recap & nominations tease -->
    <p style="margin:0 0 12px; color:#1a2744; font-size:16px; font-weight:700;">Looking Back, Looking Ahead</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#333333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">The 21st International Electoral Awards in Gaborone, Botswana last October brought together electoral leaders from across the globe to celebrate innovation and excellence in electoral administration. We are excited to build on that momentum in 2026.</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#333333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;"><strong>Nominations for the 2026 Awards will open in April.</strong> If your organisation or a colleague has delivered innovative work in electoral administration, we warmly encourage you to consider submitting a nomination. Further details on categories and the submission process will follow shortly.</p>

    <!-- Closing -->
    <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#333333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">We look forward to an engaging year ahead and hope to welcome you to Manila in November.</p>

